title: Upload assessment documents
line1: You need toÂ upload a template and instructions for the written proposal, as well as instructions for each of the additional assessment methods you have selected for this procurement.
line2: You can upload more documents on this page to give suppliers additional information.
p1: You can upload multiple files, each no larger than 300mb, to a total of 1GB.
p2: Acceptable file formats: csv, doc, docx, jpg, jpeg, kml, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, rdf, rtf, txt, xls, xlsx, xml, zip
